utions  Advertisement  Advertise with us  PARIS (AP) - As a gay youth growing up in central France, Hugo Bardin never felt he lived in a world that represented who he was - a world in which he had a place.\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 1359, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1119, \"end\": 1138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winnipeg_Free_Press\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Winnipeg Free Press\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winnipeg_Free_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winnipeg_Free_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 1203, \"end\": 1205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.118369511608019e-16, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 1246, \"end\": 1252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999049599110087, \"rank\": 5.847036826461344e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read this article for free:    Already have an account?Log in here \\u00bb  To continue reading, please subscribe:  $0 for the first 4 weeks*  *No charge for 4 weeks then price increases to the regular rate of $19.00 plus GST every four weeks.\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1598, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Offer available to new and qualified returning subscribers only.\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1663, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cancel any time.\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1680, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"$4.75/week*  *Billed as $19 plus GST every four weeks.\", \"from\": 1682, \"to\": 1736, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cancel any time.\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1753, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To continue reading, please subscribe:  $1 for the first 4 weeks*  No thanks  *Your next subscription payment will increase by $1.00 and you will be charged $16.99 plus GST for four weeks.\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1943, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After four weeks, your payment will increase to $23.99 plus GST every four weeks.\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 2025, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"PARIS (AP) - As a gay youth growing up in central France, Hugo Bardin never felt he lived in a world that represented who he was - a world in which he had a place.\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2190, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2034, \"end\": 2036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.118369511608019e-16, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 2077, \"end\": 2083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999049599110087, \"rank\": 5.847036826461344e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read unlimited articles for free today:    Already have an account?Log in here \\u00bb  Hey there, time traveller!This article was published31/07/2024(489 days ago), so information in it may no longer be current.\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2398, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"PARIS (AP) - As a gay youth growing up in central France, Hugo Bardin never felt he lived in a world that represented who he was - a world in which he had a place.\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2563, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2407, \"end\": 2409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.118369511608019e-16, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 2450, \"end\": 2456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999049599110087, \"rank\": 5.847036826461344e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that is why Bardin, who performs as the drag queen Paloma, felt it was meaningful and important to be part of a Paris Olympics opening ceremony that presented a multifaceted, multiethnic France with people of different ethnicities and orientations.\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2817, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2620, \"end\": 2626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.317560137786877e-16, \"text\": \"Paloma\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\"}, {\"begin\": 2681, \"end\": 2695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2756, \"end\": 2762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999049599110087, \"rank\": 5.847036826461344e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was a really important moment for the French people and the representation of France around the world,\\\" says Paloma, who took part in a single scene that has drawn some furious criticism - including from presidential candidate Donald Trump in the United States, who called it \\\"a disgrace.\\\"\", \"from\": 2819, \"to\": 3112, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2861, \"end\": 2874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}, {\"begin\": 2901, \"end\": 2907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999049599110087, \"rank\": 5.847036826461344e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 2932, \"end\": 2938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.317560137786877e-16, \"text\": \"Paloma\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\"}, {\"begin\": 3050, \"end\": 3062, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999999795364, \"rank\": 1.9897575825277935e-11, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 3070, \"end\": 3083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9998890898937813, \"rank\": 0.00011092240865919872, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although the ceremony's artistic director, Thomas Jolly, and other participants have repeatedly said the scene wasn't inspired by \\\"The Last Supper,\\\" critics interpreted that part of the show as a mockery of Leonardo Da Vinci's painting showing Jesus Christ and his apostles.\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3388, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3157, \"end\": 3163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\", \"score\": 0.9961359099743679, \"rank\": 0.002866564021633571, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\"}, {\"begin\": 3321, \"end\": 3329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0174636246008427e-20, \"text\": \"Leonardo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}, {\"begin\": 3330, \"end\": 3338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0937246040951185e-35, \"text\": \"Da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}, {\"begin\": 3358, \"end\": 3370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.999999999098236, \"rank\": 9.01884750532426e-10, \"text\": \"Jesus Christ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paloma, best known for winning \\\"Drag Race France,\\\" appeared with other drag artists and dancers alongside Barbara Butch, a popular DJ who wore a silver headdress that looked like a halo.\", \"from\": 3390, \"to\": 3576, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3390, \"end\": 3396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.317560137786877e-16, \"text\": \"Paloma\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\"}, {\"begin\": 3496, \"end\": 3509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"score\": 0.9999897744159937, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Barbara Butch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Butch has now filed a complaint alleging online abuse and harassment, and Paris police have launched an investigation.\", \"from\": 3577, \"to\": 3695, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3651, \"end\": 3656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3941025779054645e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paloma is not, at this point, planning to take legal action over online harassment, and would prefer to focus on the many \\\"loving messages\\\" that have been pouring in.\", \"from\": 3697, \"to\": 3863, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3697, \"end\": 3703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.317560137786877e-16, \"text\": \"Paloma\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The performer been getting thousands of messages daily, she told The Associated Press, most of them positive but some that she described as \\\"violent\\\" and even \\\"from the Middle Ages.\\\"\", \"from\": 3864, \"to\": 4046, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3933, \"end\": 3949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"score\": 0.9999999995507096, \"rank\": 4.4926651681307907e-10, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, there are no misgivings, despite the backlash.\", \"from\": 4048, \"to\": 4101, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paloma said she was proud to have been part of a show that did not rely on a series of French cliches - for example, \\\"the Parisian with a baguette under their arm.\\\"\", \"from\": 4102, \"to\": 4266, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4102, \"end\": 4108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.317560137786877e-16, \"text\": \"Paloma\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\"}, {\"begin\": 4189, \"end\": 4195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9997669803286691, \"rank\": 0.00023184569323200145, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It could have been a postcard from 1930,\\\" she said of the ceremony.\", \"from\": 4268, \"to\": 4336, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But instead, it was a photograph of France in 2024.\\\"\", \"from\": 4337, \"to\": 4390, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4374, \"end\": 4380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999049599110087, \"rank\": 5.847036826461344e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many agreed and praised the ceremony for its creativity, style and showmanship.\", \"from\": 4392, \"to\": 4471, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But French Catholic bishops and others were among those who said Christians had been offended, though Paris Olympics organizers have said there was \\\"never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group\\\" but rather to \\\"celebrate community tolerance.\\\"\", \"from\": 4473, \"to\": 4730, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4477, \"end\": 4483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9997669803286691, \"rank\": 0.00023184569323200145, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 4484, \"end\": 4492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999998932135042, \"rank\": 1.0423837890831911e-07, \"text\": \"Catholic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}, {\"begin\": 4538, \"end\": 4548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9966717687142057, \"rank\": 0.003338990157117712, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 4575, \"end\": 4589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Trump was asked on Fox News what he thought of the so-called \\\"Last Supper\\\" scene.\", \"from\": 4732, \"to\": 4813, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4732, \"end\": 4737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999986121111, \"rank\": 1.3877957791654198e-09, \"text\": \"Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 4751, \"end\": 4759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.398209357688877e-26, \"text\": \"Fox News\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am very open-minded,\\\" the former president and current Republican nominee told host Laura Ingraham, \\\"but I thought what they did was a disgrace.\\\"\", \"from\": 4814, \"to\": 4962, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4872, \"end\": 4882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Second_Spanish_Republic\", \"score\": 0.9999605774773203, \"rank\": 3.942402876007431e-05, \"text\": \"Republican\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Second_Spanish_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Second_Spanish_Republic\"}, {\"begin\": 4901, \"end\": 4915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Ingraham\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5643760699527205e-28, \"text\": \"Laura Ingraham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Ingraham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Ingraham\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of Trump's comments, Paloma said: \\\"My first reaction is to say that if Donald Trump is not reacting, then we have not done our job.\\\"\", \"from\": 4964, \"to\": 5096, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4967, \"end\": 4972, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999986121111, \"rank\": 1.3877957791654198e-09, \"text\": \"Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 4985, \"end\": 4991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.317560137786877e-16, \"text\": \"Paloma\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\"}, {\"begin\": 5035, \"end\": 5047, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999999795364, \"rank\": 1.9897575825277935e-11, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The criticism, she said, has been fueled by hate.\", \"from\": 5098, \"to\": 5147, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Where is the Catholicism, the Christianity in that?\", \"from\": 5148, \"to\": 5200, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5179, \"end\": 5191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999999609344749, \"rank\": 3.90501313526276e-08, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is very hypocritical that their message is not about religion or kindness, it's about hate towards Jews, fat people, queer people and trans people.\\\"\", \"from\": 5201, \"to\": 5352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5303, \"end\": 5307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"score\": 0.9953264652611407, \"rank\": 0.0046954717598139285, \"text\": \"Jews\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have been accused of trying to impose our vision on the world,\\\" Bardin said.\", \"from\": 5354, \"to\": 5434, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are not.\", \"from\": 5435, \"to\": 5447, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u2026 We just want to let people know that we have a place in the world, and we are claiming that place.\\\"\", \"from\": 5448, \"to\": 5549, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paloma spoke to the AP in a phone interview and later at her Paris workshop, a studio devoted to her drag performance.\", \"from\": 5551, \"to\": 5669, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5551, \"end\": 5557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.317560137786877e-16, \"text\": \"Paloma\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\"}, {\"begin\": 5571, \"end\": 5573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.118369511608019e-16, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 5612, \"end\": 5617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3941025779054645e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bardin debuted the drag queen persona some five years ago, the Spanish name inspired by the films of Pedro Almod\\u00f3var.\", \"from\": 5670, \"to\": 5787, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5733, \"end\": 5740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"score\": 0.9998702252382895, \"rank\": 0.00010781751080772018, \"text\": \"Spanish\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\"}, {\"begin\": 5771, \"end\": 5786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pedro_Almod\\u00f3var\", \"score\": 0.9999999575011325, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pedro Almod\\u00f3var\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pedro_Almod\\u00f3var\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pedro_Almod\\u00f3var\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked if she had any regrets, Paloma replied: \\\"My only regrets is people's reactions.\", \"from\": 5789, \"to\": 5874, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5819, \"end\": 5825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.317560137786877e-16, \"text\": \"Paloma\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am sorry if people are offended, but we did not try to parody, to mock 'The Last Supper.'\", \"from\": 5875, \"to\": 5966, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was not the point.\", \"from\": 5967, \"to\": 5988, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I can not regret what I did.\", \"from\": 5989, \"to\": 6020, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am sorry for people to only see things in a bad way.\\\"\", \"from\": 6021, \"to\": 6076, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thursdays  Keep up to date on sports with Mike McIntyre's weekly newsletter.\", \"from\": 6078, \"to\": 6154, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6120, \"end\": 6133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_McIntyre\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mike McIntyre\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_McIntyre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_McIntyre\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She added: \\\"Maybe change the perspective.\", \"from\": 6156, \"to\": 6197, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Change the point of view.\", \"from\": 6198, \"to\": 6223, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Try to see the beauty in what we did.\", \"from\": 6224, \"to\": 6261, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Because it was just beauty.\", \"from\": 6262, \"to\": 6289, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was just only about beauty and reunion, and reparation.\\\"\", \"from\": 6290, \"to\": 6349, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"___  AP journalists Nicolas Garriga and Amira Borders in Paris contributed to this report.\", \"from\": 6